      <textAnnotation id="sid-E7292F15-A3D6-41BB-B76E-7AD2BB0E5013" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Process Tower : OTC - Order To Cash
Process Group: Order Management
Process: O-060-140 Inform Plant/Warehouse of Order Change/Cancellation</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-7DDB1665-4429-48E0-A884-E7CBA49F0D2D" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-450991AF-FF79-4A1D-B5A1-2D78DE9E816F" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-038E88C4-A6B7-4F99-82FB-9097ED32B6B0" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>DN cancelation is only an
exception process. Any
changes within order
modification window can
only be conducted by super
user.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-6C572670-FE7F-4A95-8AF7-B11A3B9E234F" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Logistics WRAPPER
program will create a
Delivery note for SO1
when DN2 will PGI</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-D1169BE7-9B30-4906-9B06-25F0984B7097" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>LCSR request is
required on
DN2. However SO1 and
SO2 SOLI require a Intel
hold.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-CF001A8F-B24F-4936-A3C1-A04A10ADA906" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-9039633E-4C8D-471D-8BD9-55BD0DF8A268" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-C08F2DD6-335A-4030-BD13-1235A0C9ACD1" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1.3PL WH will send a 3B14C with Accept or Reject as a response back to LCSR
2.WH operator must also check SO2 status and determine if SO1 LCSR DN cancelation can be cancelled or not</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-4753EDD9-A8EA-4D4C-A263-9EAC056621BA" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-01B4C3B1-F992-4264-90F7-5B9C9BFEA474" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="true" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="24.0" italic="" ref="text-left"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="true" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="24.0" italic="" ref="text-right"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Flow has been migrated to BIC. Please inform Process Steward:  Sandhu, Anita &lt;anita.sandhu@intel.com&gt;, and BPM Champion: Rebeca, Meza Redondo &lt;rebeca.meza.redondo@intel.com&gt; of any changes that occur within the flow from now onwards so that changes can be accurately reflected within BIC</text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
